WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.610 --> 00:00:03.070
- I wanna congratulate
you on being a person

00:00:03.070 --> 00:00:05.430
that's always looking
for the cutting edge.

00:00:05.430 --> 00:00:06.540
For you to be exposed

00:00:06.540 --> 00:00:07.910
to what we're doing here at OsteoStrong,

00:00:07.910 --> 00:00:09.820
you literally are on the cutting edge

00:00:09.820 --> 00:00:12.260
of the best technologies
to change the human body

00:00:12.260 --> 00:00:13.930
in the shortest period of time.

00:00:13.930 --> 00:00:15.340
I just wanted to say to you

00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:17.520
that as you join the OsteoStrong here,

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:18.680
you've gotten involved in this.

00:00:18.680 --> 00:00:20.750
You have got yourself exposed

00:00:20.750 --> 00:00:23.100
to one of the greatest tools
that I've ever seen in my life.

00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:24.330
I'm involved with the company

00:00:24.330 --> 00:00:28.310
because my wife, Sage, and I
have done this for five years.

00:00:28.310 --> 00:00:30.680
And my wife normally would not exercise

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:33.280
consistently with anything,
but she's totally addicted.

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:34.370
Because with OsteoStrong,

00:00:34.370 --> 00:00:37.650
you're talking about 60
seconds of real exercise.

00:00:37.650 --> 00:00:39.320
And wait, there's four machines.

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:42.250
It's about 15 minutes of actual exertion.

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:44.230
So you got a minute of exercise a week,

00:00:44.230 --> 00:00:46.940
and yet you keep getting
stronger and stronger.

00:00:46.940 --> 00:00:48.610
So you have an opportunity

00:00:48.610 --> 00:00:50.090
to do something no one else has done,

00:00:50.090 --> 00:00:51.930
which is have the right dosage.

00:00:51.930 --> 00:00:53.850
The minimum amount of exercise

00:00:53.850 --> 00:00:55.460
for the maximum amount of growth.

00:00:55.460 --> 00:00:58.100
You're gonna use enormous force,

00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:00.250
but not put yourself in any form of danger

00:01:00.250 --> 00:01:02.640
'cause you're not lifting
a 500 pound weight.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:04.080
We're using the power of these computers

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:06.040
to monitor you and give you this progress.

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:07.840
And we're unleashing

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:09.800
what will allow you to have strong bones,

00:01:09.800 --> 00:01:11.640
and more importantly, equally importantly,

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:13.890
the kind of fitness,
agility, and strength,

00:01:13.890 --> 00:01:15.900
and energy that you really want.

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:17.380
Because when the bones are strong,

00:01:17.380 --> 00:01:19.550
the muscles that are
attached are stronger.

00:01:19.550 --> 00:01:22.350
Everything comes from what
we start here at OsteoStrong.

